ctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(context.Background(), time.Second)
defer cancel()

response, err := client.Users.ListWithCursorPagination(
	ctx,
	&fern.ListUsersCursorPaginationRequest{
		Page:          1,
		PerPage:       1,
		Order:         fern.OrderAsc,
		StartingAfter: "string",
	},
)

	&fern.ListUsersOffsetPaginationRequest{

		Order:         fern.OrderAsc,
		StartingAfter: "string",
	},
)
